name: The Confession
description: I used to think that heart is the most a fragile thing that human have. Now, I dont feel anything. I lost it since the first time somebody I love and I trust just kick my stomach, slap my cheek, and put a lemonad on to my scars. It's hurt, but I don't hurt back, because I am now being a numb dumb. I just keep writing a poem, even no one understand.
